{"tid":567294,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李慧詩贏女子競輪賽盡攬3金   港隊5金完美謝幕","createTime":"2018-02-20T17:27:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-21T18:53:50.000Z","uid":79563,"like":40,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"8c6c3102d3bce892b6c17c1d8f26587f9f19e828","tid":567294,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T17:27:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20180220/s00006/f9fb7245913464fd53d78c87fa8a073e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20180220%2Fs00006%2Ff9fb7245913464fd53d78c87fa8a073e.jpg&h=a7e36573&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n繼張敬樂伙梁峻榮在麥迪遜重奪金牌，「牛下女車神」李慧詩（Sarah）緊接在凱林賽（又稱競輪賽），力壓韓國車手李慧貞，壓軸為港以5金在場地單車亞洲賽完美收官，更是連續兩年包攬個人短距離3金。<br />\n<br />\n復出僅1個月的港隊星將李慧詩，日前先後奪走500米計時賽及爭先賽金牌，今日在壓軸上演的女子凱林賽再度發威，連過2關殺入決賽，最終力壓韓國老對手李慧貞，輕鬆封后，更是她出戰3項全部袋走金牌。另一港將刁小娟在女子捕捉賽，則僅負中華台北主將黃亭茵，屈居銀牌，亦是前者個人第2面銀牌。港隊在大年初一起連戰5天，最終以5金5銀2銅謝幕，突破去屆5金3銀3銅成績，而李慧詩、刁小娟、梁峻榮及張敬樂4名獎牌功臣，稍後將與女將楊倩玉及李海恩轉赴荷蘭，出戰下周四展開的場地單車世界賽。"},{"pid":"be18a2ac76aeb9961c0613e06191650570f1720a","tid":567294,"uid":38904,"like":10,"dislike":16,"score":-6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-20T17:29:22.000Z","msg":"條友撐呂麗瑤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown2.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89f1d3517ccab8a9823796d07278cca0ed343e6c","tid":567294,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T17:02:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b96949cff8ab7b536d554b5331aa2b048c309b1e","tid":567294,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-21T17:03:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/devil.gif\" class=\"hk